  chapter: 9
  number: 37
  title: Underwater Mining
  description: "Dive deep beneath the ocean in your submarine to recover alien fuel
    crystals scattered across the seabed. Strong water currents and dangerous underwater
    mines make navigation tricky\u2014precision and timing are key to survival."
  objectives: 'Collect 10 alien fuel crystals hidden underwater.


    Maintain control
    of the submarine by managing air pressure to rise or sink.


    Avoid collisions
    with underwater mines and obstacles.'
  scoring: 
  bronzeObjective: 
  silverObjective: 
