  - icon: 4
    name: Chapter 9 - Post Test
    description: Fluid Mechanics
  - icon: 3
    name: Freeplay > Minigame 9
    description: Underwater Mining
  instructions: "1. Use (+) Add Air to rise and (-) Remove Air to sink.\n\n2. Steer
    carefully to collect crystals while avoiding hazards.\n\n3. Keep an eye on the
    Air in the Tank bar\u2014too little or too much air can affect stability.\n\n4.
    Gather all crystals before time runs out to complete the mission!\n\nNote: The
    game ends if the submarine hits any obstacle or if time runs out before collecting
    all crystals. Collect 10/10 crystals successfully while keeping your submarine
    intact."
